    • findNextAvailableChannel

      private String findNextAvailableChannel(edu.uiowa.cs.warp.ProgramSchedule schedule, String nodeName, Integer currentTime, Integer srcNodeIndex, Integer snkNodeIndex)
      Finds next available channel and returns the name of that channel. If no channel was available will return UNKNOWN. Caller will need to verify.
      Parameters:
      schedule - for the whole program
      nodeName - name of the current node
      currentTime - current valid time of the program
      srcNodeIndex - the current index of src node
      snkNodeIndex - the current index of the snk node
      Returns:
      name of the next available channel as a string
